WEBVTT

22:07.774 --> 22:10.149
Are you trying to tempt someone
who isn't even interested?

22:11.108 --> 22:13.983
Didn't she already say she doesn't want
anyone expecting a dowry?

22:14.274 --> 22:15.566
This isn't dowry, dear...

22:15.733 --> 22:17.108
-It's her share.
-Hah!

22:17.149 --> 22:18.149
It's the same thing!

22:18.858 --> 22:21.358
Dad, can't you at least try
to understand what we're saying?
